{"tid":1776520,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀lunch食開咩?","createTime":"2019-12-09T15:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T10:24:13.000Z","uid":104804,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"3a525d2ff372aa66de695f09afa470a90210b7b9","tid":1776520,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:01:59.000Z","msg":"龍門光榮味道一般<br />\n成日有人排隊咁打算懲罰下其他店<br />\n以前都有去開鐵火堂(唔知咩立場唔得閒去)沙嗲王(藍已經無去)<br />\n呢排真係唔知食咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日都只係買左個叉燒包食出奇地好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419b8532753be7a95ad850b5530ae7953f970cbe","tid":1776520,"uid":118843,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:20:11.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀好多黃店喎"},{"pid":"9e94f5693bf4bd3d21b41d3c662a937d6ab2d282","tid":1776520,"uid":121265,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:24:37.000Z","msg":"嘉寶漢堡"},{"pid":"627f64e3823560c17ba9ca95075b819e338d294e","tid":1776520,"uid":308915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e94f5693bf4bd3d21b41d3c662a937d6ab2d282","tid":1776520,"uid":121265,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:24:37.000Z","msg":"嘉寶漢堡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:25:49.000Z","msg":"呢間個舖位好細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2f23ee586bc221070aece1232839a37b8233f4","tid":1776520,"uid":104804,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"419b8532753be7a95ad850b5530ae7953f970cbe","tid":1776520,"uid":118843,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:20:11.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀好多黃店喎"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:58:21.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n我見有幾間都樓上鋪<br />\n好驚一個人唔敢上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次去光榮叫何已完之後有個女仔搭檯<br />\n佢又係叫何已完<br />\n佢坐底一陣個侍應比左佢先<br />\n我無出聲佢又食左<br />\n十分鐘後終於到我啦<br />\n個女仔望住我<br />\n我又望住佢好尷尬<br />\n拿拿聲食完就埋單走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇中一間潮丸諗住一陣試下"},{"pid":"111b327deea0a3dfcdd902a8a6a3385329c635a4","tid":1776520,"uid":61267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef2f23ee586bc221070aece1232839a37b8233f4","tid":1776520,"uid":104804,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"419b8532753be7a95ad850b5530ae7953f970cbe","tid":1776520,"uid":118843,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:20:11.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀好多黃店喎"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:58:21.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n我見有幾間都樓上鋪<br />\n好驚一個人唔敢上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次去光榮叫何已完之後有個女仔搭檯<br />\n佢又係叫何已完<br />\n佢坐底一陣個侍應比左佢先<br />\n我無出聲佢又食左<br />\n十分鐘後終於到我啦<br />\n個女仔望住我<br />\n我又望住佢好尷尬<br />\n拿拿聲食完就埋單走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇中一間潮丸諗住一陣試下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:37:43.000Z","msg":"潮丸幾好  下午茶仲8折  <br />\n幾抵食"},{"pid":"7dd963647adacffd02e0279e9d8669194a37a5ea","tid":1776520,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:53:15.000Z","msg":"interpeninsula"},{"pid":"47f1f21e1ec9f3dfaa74c99d9ba40089e94b705b","tid":1776520,"uid":332036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T17:08:24.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"c036d5e2936819182ade847b5b167b93a03615e5","tid":1776520,"uid":332036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"有時頹到去donki買外賣 但又幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a62a4491edb9bbb4f10ac9227ce59f0c9b3223","tid":1776520,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c036d5e2936819182ade847b5b167b93a03615e5","tid":1776520,"uid":332036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"有時頹到去donki買外賣 但又幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T17:15:01.000Z","msg":"其實幾好食<br />\n但有時凍冰冰或者焗到