oji\" />"},{"pid":"2fcadab6aa7e34f22f64b339606d750e84a4e948","tid":1776520,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T08:22:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係<br />\n我見有幾間都樓上鋪<br />\n好驚一個人唔敢上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次去光榮叫何已完之後有個女仔搭檯<br />\n佢又係叫何已完<br />\n佢坐底一陣個侍應比左佢先<br />\n我無出聲佢又食左<br />\n十分鐘後終於到我啦<br />\n個女仔望住我<br />\n我又望住佢好尷尬<br />\n拿拿聲食完就埋單走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇中一間潮丸諗住一陣試下</blockquote>即係個女仔唔靚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>扑左未</blockquote>今日又食左  佢d牛爽腩真係幾好食</blockquote><br />\n食左八折係抵既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n味道都幾好<br />\n唔知係唔係下午茶時段<br />\n覺得好多員工咁<br />\n做野好快手<br />\n食到我好緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次再試下其他<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XuLOoHU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXuLOoHU.jpg&h=ce8ebafc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩又食左<br />\n要左粗麵好重咩水味<br />\n都係河粉好食d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14910da8fe3d8861173d0eaed2bf724d1d35a9d0","tid":1776520,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"重慶大廈食咖哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93d6ca034723bc873279101617ea3d9b540db6d","tid":1776520,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14910da8fe3d8861173d0eaed2bf724d1d35a9d0","tid":1776520,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"重慶大廈食咖哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T08:31:24.000Z","msg